2. Determine the correct revset (e.g., `author("Bob") & ~::main & ::@`).
3. Write it to `revset.txt`: `echo 'author("Bob") & ~::main & ::@' > revset.txt` (or whatever the correct query is).

## Constraints
- Project path: `/home/user/project`.
